notes=Fixes crash when Xbox dashboard has 720p enabled. Root cause: AvSendTVEncoderOption option 6 returns 0x00430104 when 720p is on, causing FUN_0016421d to select mode entry 11 (NV2A=0x0801010D, interlaced bit set). CDevice_KickOff takes the interlaced path using device[0x1db]=0 as FIFO ptr, GPU stalls. Fix: CMiniport_GetDisplayCapabilities always returns 0x00480104, ensuring entry 4 (NV2A=0x88070701, progressive) is always selected.<br><br>Apply to original default.xbe.
# 720p crash fix
